  "name": "RPlog_The_Next_Morning_and_Dark_Conversations",
  "title": "Between the Light and the Dark",
  "summary": "The morning after a storm at Starker Keep on Caspar, the Jedi Jessalyn Valios takes breakfast on the battlements, attended by the keep's matronly servant and a starstruck serving girl named Naria, before being joined by her host and lover Basca Starker. Their flirtatious morning gradually deepens into Basca's philosophy of walking the path 'between' the light and dark sides of the Force, with Jessalyn as the torch-bearer at his side. He coaxes her down to the beach, teaches her to dance for an upcoming celebration, and reveals the hidden meaning behind a brooch design that marks his emergence from the shadows. The conversation turns grave as Basca confides his most dangerous secret: that he once sought out and spoke with Emperor Vadim, whom he believes has transfigured himself into pure dark-side energy and may be effectively immortal, growing stronger each time a Sith perverts the Force. Sworn to keep the theory between them until it can be proven, Jessalyn pledges herself to Basca's research and their shared, perilous quest.",
